item.title: Current Members with Access
item.dc:creator: @wL1 wL
item.description:
@wL1 wrote:

Nice list, a couple of names associate to some nice memories

I happen to log into this forum maybe once a year, which is about the frequency with which I’m suddenly overcome with an odd feeling of curiosity. I guess it is triggered by something more or less remotely related to my RS past and thus reminds me of it. Anyways, I still get PMs, some of which I answer, but other than that, I don’t have much to say that would be of major relevance to you guys.

Greetings from evo/winterLove
